oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ON SINGING GARDENS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Swan, Lawrence W.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: I represent several areas of concern regarding theimportation of exotic animals into the United States.I am primarily a Professor of Biology, a zoogeographerand ecologist, and I am well aware of the history andecology of alien species. As a Director of the SanFrancisco Zoological Society and involved in educationaland research programs at the San Francisco Zoo,I have a deep interest in the functions of zoos. I amalso involved in aviculture both as a research zoologistand as a breeder of birds.
